{"tid":1247314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"親中團體［加碼]，今贈果籃及一百萬元撑警","createTime":"2019-06-21T05:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T17:31:53.000Z","uid":185781,"like":187,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"250b548c2f4a7564c7c2794b0b9696f7c5ac38d2","tid":1247314,"uid":185781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOoi7w4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOoi7w4.png&h=29d7d840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBRXDEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBRXDEw.png&h=4c8fd5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【10:00】近日反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行及集會釀警民衝突，有團體今日（21日）在灣仔警署總部向警察送上感謝信及捐贈100萬元，並表示對近日的警民衝突感痛心。<br />\n<br />\n港區省級政協委員聯誼會與香港政協青年聯會約30名會員於今早10時，於灣仔警察總部聚集，大叫「阿Sir辛苦晒」、「我哋支持香港警察」等口號；他們向警方送上感謝信，並向警察福利基金捐贈100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員、港區省級政協委員聯誼會會長施榮懷表示，近日的遊行集會上雖然大部分是和平示威者，但有個別人士衝擊警方，他對此感到痛心；至於應否成立獨立委員會調查警方於6‧12的行動，他認為可由政府、監警會等「香港原有、行之有效的機制處理」，並認為大家的眼睛是雪亮的，希望可還警方一個公道。另外，他說捐贈款項由兩會會費撥出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190621/s00001/1561085750574/【逃犯條例】多個團體警總遞信支持執法-捐百萬感謝警方\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561085750574%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E9%81%9E%E4%BF%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E6%8D%90%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=0042b99c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561085750574%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E9%81%9E%E4%BF%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-%E6%8D%90%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9&h=1a387185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190621/s00001/1561085750574/【逃犯條例】多個團體警總遞信支持執法-捐百萬感謝警方</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【11:00】近11時，珍惜群組約20名市民亦於灣仔警署總部支持警方執法，他們大叫「警察執法被屈」、「感謝警察 盡忠職守」等口號，又向警方代表送上飲品及小食，讓警方補充體力。珍惜群組召集人李璧表示，對近日遊行集會感到痛心疾首，批評學校教學生違法達義，又指示威者蒙面似早有預備，令警方執法時有畏懼。"},{"pid":"527afb06cc3d38bbd70c7d630791f9d67b717bec","tid":1247314,"uid":185781,"like":213,"dislike":1,"score":212,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"上次淨係送三萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b69063dd1bc878fa994ac52992a77f78d519be","tid":1247314,"uid":45830,"like":309,"dislike":0,"score":309,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"你老味，個果藍咁L 細，又要call 梁國雄議員"},{"pid":"7febbec8794acb278409e706c78371aaa03c0840","tid":1247314,"uid":78039,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"c5b69063dd1bc878fa994ac52992a77f78d519be","tid":1247314,"uid":45830,"like":309,"dislike":0,"score":309,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"你老味，個果藍咁L 細，又要call 梁國雄議員"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"夠邊個食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e368d389fa8b61e6419ad6b276c77935ec5666","tid":1247314,"uid":185781,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"c5b69063dd1bc878fa994ac52992a77f78d519be","tid":1247314,"uid":45830,"like":309,"dislike":0,"score":309,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"你老味，個果藍咁L 細，又要call 梁國雄議員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"原來香港咁多政協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔見福建春哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872e5194b9d85a0351a52636e86d332598627090","tid":1247314,"uid":185781,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7febbec8794acb278409e706c78371aaa03c0840","tid":1247314,"uid":78039,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"c5b69063dd1bc878fa994ac52992a77f